                                                                                                    information we
                                                                                                    already have on
                                                                                                    file, or we may
                                                                                                    contact you through
                                                                                                    a communication
                                                                                                    method (e.g.
,
phone or
                                                                                                    email) that you have
                                                                                                    previously provided
                                                                                                    to us. We may also
                                                                                                    use other
                                                                                                    verification methods
                                                                                                    as the circumstances
                                                                                                    dictate.
